About Me

Hi there, my name is Pablo Prieto and I am a senior at the City College of New York pursuing a B.E in Computer Engineering. I am currently interning at NYC's HRA managing the databases using mySQL and generating reports and summaries for the data required. I have worked in projects of all types, from data structures, algorithms, software design and API's to designing logic gates for semiconductors and creating latches to learn the concepts behind processors.

Languages that I am proficient in include, C, C++, Java, Assembly Language, JavaScript, SQL, and HTML. I am greatly efficient with object oriented programming and have an interest for web and app design. Currently, I am working on learning app design and have already created some simple apps.
